{"id": "QmVPGX8NmzWxCRFmyCYnD9f4MZQhQzMndim5i4FqxqTgNC", "title": "Bind Referral Reward to 1% Payback", "body": "Proposed to adjust the referral reward amount:\n\n1. Bind the referral reward amount to 1% payback from the staked amount. Referral reward amount in LDO to be calculated each payout week based on ETH/USD and LDO/USD 14 days (whole referral period) TWAP to be 1% payback;\n2. Limit minimum referral amount to 5 LDO for 1 ETH staked.\n3. Limit maximum referral amount to 20 LDO for 1 ETH staked.\nUpdated reward amount to take effect at the next referral period after DAO voting.\n\nLink to the forum discussion: https://research.lido.fi/t/bind-referral-reward-to-1-payback/1021\n\nMotivation\nCurrently, the referral reward amount is 15 LDO for 1 ETH which is 2.4% payback (based on 14 days TWAP of LDO and ETH, see calculations below). Initial payback was ~1% at the date of the referral program launch. The referral reward amount is the key parameter that needs to be adjusted. Linking referral reward to 1% payback will help to use the rewarding budget most effectively, make the calculation process clear and transparent, keeping the referral program profitable and reaching the goals.\n\n", "choices": ["Bind Referral Reward to 1%", "Leave static 15 LDO reward"], "start": 1631016900, "end": 1631380800, "snapshot": "13178454", "state": "closed", "author": "0x7A43968AaC869eB48D88563Fad072fEF8ED76343", "space": {"id": "lido-snapshot.eth", "name": "Lido"}, "votes": 17, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmNjtJtLRB9yg2Ngmeiy3sYQy3dGJgADXtUrGpya1prrdV", "voter": "0x31d173Ea66Fa8fBa38b3DDB798C1c1098f3AE8c5", "created": 1631378403, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "lido-snapshot.eth"}}, {"id": "QmVf2qWDiTV97Y3V3arj3wXHCJrA23nDFhN59TppivB4e6", "voter": "0xC54570b8EB8138aCE95132b944b7b6Bb391976Dc", "created": 1631368190, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "lido-snapshot.eth"}}, {"id": "QmSj7ShF2G6ifd7p1hQDNJyhnpy6D33aoo8C4WqwDs4hb7", "voter": "0x698048A913c9Bf5Df4DE96542c3cDA6BB8D60Cf6", "created": 1